♪Jangan pernah mundur♪

30
00:01:42,180 --> 00:01:44,890
♪Ketika kenyataan
menghadapi jalan buntu♪

31
00:01:44,890 --> 00:01:47,390
♪Keputusasaan menjerat harapan♪

32
00:01:47,390 --> 00:01:51,100
♪Juga masih tersenyum acuh tak acuh♪

33
00:01:53,060 --> 00:01:55,510
♪Palu di kiri melindungi rumput
di tangan kanan♪

34
00:01:55,510 --> 00:01:58,260
♪Roh pelindung ganda dihunuskan♪

35
00:01:58,260 --> 00:02:01,680
♪Melawan situasi putus asa♪

36
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:04,010
♪Juga tak akan pernah mundur♪

37
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:09,910
(Animasi ini diadaptasi dari novel
Tang Jia San Shao "Douluo Dalu")

38
00:02:11,710 --> 00:02:13,617
(Cuplikan episode sebelumnya)
Kau kira sudah…

39
00:02:13,617 --> 00:02:15,380
…menyelesaikan proses
menjadi naga,…

40
00:02:15,380 --> 00:02:18,350
…sudah bisa melawan keagunganku?

41
00:02:18,350 --> 00:02:21,080
Karena kultivasimu selama
bertahun-tahun tidaklah mudah,…

42
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,750
…aku ampuni lagi nyawamu.

43
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:27,210
Semoga pilihan kali ini
tak mengecewakanku.

44
00:02:27,210 --> 00:02:28,780
Terima kasih sudah
menyelamatkanku.

45
00:02:28,780 --> 00:02:30,050
Aku berutang nyawa padamu.

46
00:02:30,450 --> 00:02:31,210
Berhasil.

47
00:02:31,810 --> 00:02:34,380
Kekuatan rohku sudah
menembus level 67.

48
00:02:34,380 --> 00:02:35,750
Caramu tadi butuh kekuatan roh.

49
00:02:35,750 --> 00:02:37,150
Aku terlahir tanpa kekuatan roh.

50
00:02:37,150 --> 00:02:39,810
Bagaimana jika aku bisa membuatmu
meningkatkan kekuatan rohmu?

51
00:02:40,410 --> 00:02:41,150
Kamu…

52
00:02:41,350 --> 00:02:42,380
Kau bilang apa?

53
00:02:43,110 --> 00:02:47,810
=Episode 166=

54
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:52,450
Kamu…

55
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:53,580
Kau bilang apa?

56
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:56,510
Aku bisa mengajarimu
sebuah cara berlatih.

57
00:02:56,510 --> 00:02:58,980
Mungkin bisa membuatmu
jadi Master Roh.

58
00:02:59,650 --> 00:03:02,210
Namun, aku tak bisa
asal mengajari.

59
00:03:02,210 --> 00:03:04,210
Kau bersedia berguru padaku?

60
00:03:06,410 --> 00:03:07,650
Aku bersedia.

61
00:03:07,850 --> 00:03:08,680
Baik.

62
00:03:10,210 --> 00:03:10,950
Guru.

63
00:03:10,950 --> 00:03:14,080
Kelak kau adalah orang sekte Tang.

64
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,250
Sekte Tang?

65
00:03:23,150 --> 00:03:23,850
Ini.

66
00:03:24,580 --> 00:03:25,850
Langsung makan.

67
00:03:27,410 --> 00:03:28,780
Raja Ginseng Puluhan Ribu Tahun?

68
00:03:29,580 --> 00:03:31,010
Ini adalah pusaka tak ternilai.

69
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,210
Ia bisa bantu
pelatihan dasarmu.

70
00:03:33,850 --> 00:03:37,450
Raja Ginseng Puluhan Ribu Tahun,
Ginseng Kristal Darah Naga,…

71
00:03:37,450 --> 00:03:40,450
…dan Raja Ginseng Tingkat Sembilan
diambil dari Mata Air Es-Api.

72
00:03:40,450 --> 00:03:45,250
Meski harganya jauh berbeda,
tapi kebetulan cocok bagi Ji Xiang.

73
00:03:46,250 --> 00:03:47,250
Duduk.

74
00:03:48,810 --> 00:03:49,880
Pertahankan tubuh.

75
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:52,710
Rasakan kekuatan roh yang
kupindahkan ke tubuhmu.

76
00:03:53,010 --> 00:03:54,980
Ingat jalan perpindahannya.

77
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:10,650
Guru.

78
00:04:10,650 --> 00:04:11,380
Lihat.

79
00:04:12,310 --> 00:04:13,250
Sangat bagus.

80
00:04:13,250 --> 00:04:14,350
Kau sangat berbakat.

81
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,850
Namun,…

82
00:04:15,850 --> 00:04:18,780
…untuk mencapai keberhasilan,
harus latihan dengan giat.

83
00:04:18,780 --> 00:04:19,550
Iya.

84
00:04:19,550 --> 00:04:20,310
Akan saya lakukan.

85
00:04:20,310 --> 00:04:21,250
Terima kasih.

86
00:04:23,050 --> 00:04:23,650
Ji Xiang.

87
00:04:24,110 --> 00:04:26,910
Seperti apa Kapten Kelompok
Bajak Laut Mutiara Ungu?

88
00:04:27,780 --> 00:04:29,510
Aku cukup kenal dengan
ketua mereka.

89
00:04:29,850 --> 00:04:30,810
Dia sangat baik.

90
00:04:31,010 --> 00:04:32,810
Sering memberi uang pada
nelayan miskin.

91
00:04:34,050 --> 00:04:36,280
Apakah kau kenal Haider?

92
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,990
Apa hubungannya dengan
Kelompok Bajak Laut Mutiara Ungu?

93
00:04:39,450 --> 00:04:40,510
Aku tahu.

94
00:04:41,010 --> 00:04:43,910
Dia bawa banyak master roh masuk
Kelompok Bajak Laut Mutiara Ungu.

95
00:04:44,350 --> 00:04:46,710
Karena itu dia selalu sombong
saat bersama kelompoknya.

96
00:04:50,550 --> 00:04:51,510
Begitukah?

97
00:04:52,250 --> 00:04:56,350
Jika aku ingin bayar mereka bantu
aku cari rekanku yang terpisah,…

98
00:04:56,350 --> 00:04:57,550
…apakah kau bisa kenalkan?

99
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,180
Tak masalah.

100
00:05:00,450 --> 00:05:01,790
Besok pagi saya bawa Anda ke sana.

101
00:05:10,350 --> 00:05:11,280
Guru.

102
00:05:11,710 --> 00:05:14,050
Kelompok Bajak Laut Mutiara Ungu
ada 3.000-an orang.

103
00:05:14,450 --> 00:05:16,050
Di antaranya ada 200 Master Roh.

104
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,950
Yang paling kuat
adalah Ketua Mutiara Ungu.

105
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,580
Kaisar Roh level 68.

106
00:05:20,950 --> 00:05:24,580
Punya 40-an kapal, sangat terkenal
di daerah lautan sekitar sini.

107
00:05:24,580 --> 00:05:25,380
Oh.

108
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:31,310
Dokter Ji Xiang.

109
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:32,380
Apa kabar, Dokter Ji Xiang.

110
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:33,850
Dokter Ji Xiang.

111
00:05:33,850 --> 00:05:35,250
Ayo minum arak bersama malam ini.

112
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:35,850
Iya.

113
00:05:35,850 --> 00:05:37,010
Haha.

114
00:05:40,110 --> 00:05:41,450
Itu adalah tempat tinggal Ketua.

115
00:05:51,410 --> 00:05:52,050
Guru.

116
00:05:52,050 --> 00:05:52,510
Kamu!

117
00:05:57,450 --> 00:05:58,180
Kak San.

118
00:05:58,180 --> 00:05:58,910
Rongrong.

119
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:00,980
Xiao San.

120
00:06:01,550 --> 00:06:02,750
Baguslah kau baik-baik saja.

121
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,250
Kami selalu khawatir padamu.

122
00:06:04,250 --> 00:06:05,380
Di mana Xiao Wu?

123
00:06:06,710 --> 00:06:08,510
Siapa yang mengikat kalian di sini?

124
00:06:12,710 --> 00:06:13,480
Guru.

125
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:15,910
Ming… Minggir.

126
00:06:17,850 --> 00:06:19,310
Gu… Guru.

127
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:24,000
Xiao Wu.

128
00:06:24,910 --> 00:06:25,610
Kak San.

129
00:06:25,610 --> 00:06:26,750
Jangan… Jangan salah paham!

130
00:06:31,010 --> 00:06:32,310
Matilah.

131
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:34,710
Siapa?

132
00:06:38,110 --> 00:06:39,410
Seorang wanita?

133
00:06:39,810 --> 00:06:41,950
Berani arogan
di Kelompok Bajak Laut Mutiara Ungu.

134
00:06:42,310 --> 00:06:43,450
Sudah bosan hidup!

135
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,680
Lepaskan, Xiao Wu.

136
00:06:45,050 --> 00:06:46,950
Jika tidak, kau tak bisa hidup lagi.

137
00:06:48,110 --> 00:06:51,050
Aku mau lihat bagaimana
kau membunuhku.

138
00:06:54,310 --> 00:06:55,383
Teknik roh ke-4!

139
00:07:00,700 --> 00:07:02,210
Kemarahan Ular Laut!

140
00:07:08,210 --> 00:07:10,010
Tak boleh melukai Xiao Wu.

141
00:07:11,050 --> 00:07:13,580
Harus segera menghindarinya.

142
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:18,750
Teknik roh ke-5,
Tombak Raja Biru Perak.

143
00:07:23,150 --> 00:07:23,950
Bos Dai.

144
00:07:27,110 --> 00:07:28,680
Kenapa dia tiba-tiba
muncul di sini?

145
00:07:42,610 --> 00:07:44,650
Guru, jangan bunuh dia!

146
00:07:49,210 --> 00:07:50,680
Kau berani menyerang ketua kami.

147
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:52,150
Kami lawan kamu!

148
00:07:52,850 --> 00:07:54,680
Dia melukai rekanku.

149
00:07:54,950 --> 00:07:56,350
Pantas mati!

150
00:07:57,010 --> 00:07:58,050
Kak San.

151
00:07:59,850 --> 00:08:02,750
Ketua Mutiara Ungu
tak melukai kami.

152
00:08:06,810 --> 00:08:07,480
Gendut.

153
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,480
Ada apa dengan mereka?

154
00:08:08,710 --> 00:08:10,480
Kami terkena racun es.

155
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,280
Dia mengikat kami di luar…

156
00:08:12,780 --> 00:08:15,410
…demi menghilangkan racun
dengan sinar matahari.

157
00:08:16,050 --> 00:08:17,580
Dia sedang menyelamatkan kami.

158
00:08:17,580 --> 00:08:18,510
Yang benar saja.

159
00:08:18,510 --> 00:08:19,410
Selamatkan apanya?

160
00:08:19,410 --> 00:08:21,010
Aku sedang menyiksa mereka.

161
00:08:21,010 --> 00:08:22,010
Lanjutkan!

162
00:08:22,010 --> 00:08:22,910
Siapa takut?

163
00:08:24,710 --> 00:08:26,080
Sebenarnya ada apa?

164
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:30,710
Sejak berpisah, kami terus
terombang-ambing di atas laut.

165
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:58,380
Lalu, kami bertemu monster roh
puluhan ribu tahun lagi.

166
00:09:18,350 --> 00:09:27,410
=Dunia Roh=

167
00:09:32,380 --> 00:09:33,250
Xiang Xiang!

168
00:09:39,780 --> 00:09:40,710
Hati-hati di dalam air!

169
00:09:41,350 --> 00:09:43,410
Rongrong! Cepat raih tanganku!

170
00:09:59,650 --> 00:10:01,150
Gelombang Cahaya Harimau Putih.

171
00:10:06,710 --> 00:10:08,810
Hati-hati. Serangannya ada racun.

172
00:10:09,950 --> 00:10:10,980
Rongrong, hati-hati!

173
00:10:36,410 --> 00:10:38,050
Sosis Kaca Penyalin!

174
00:10:45,250 --> 00:10:47,010
Meteor Phoenix!

175
00:10:55,580 --> 00:10:57,850
Teknik Tulang Roh
Lengan Kanan Api Phoenix.

176
00:11:03,010 --> 00:11:05,010
Ledakan Phoenix!

177
00:11:10,310 --> 00:11:11,380
Rasa dingin ini…

178
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:16,750
Bos Dai!

179
00:11:18,210 --> 00:11:19,750
Oscar.

180
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:26,910
Jangan kemari.

181
00:11:29,410 --> 00:11:33,150
Setelah memaksa membunuhnya,
kami terkena racun esnya.

182
00:11:33,410 --> 00:11:36,180
Bahkan api phoenix-ku juga
tak bisa mencairkannya.

183
00:11:37,850 --> 00:11:41,150
Lalu, Ketua Mutiara Ungu yang
menyelamatkan kami.

184
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,280
Gendut!

185
00:11:56,980 --> 00:12:00,050
Monster Roh puluhan ribu tahun
yang mereka temui…

186
00:12:00,050 --> 00:12:02,050
…sama seperti roh pelindung
ketua kami.

187
00:12:02,410 --> 00:12:04,150
Namanya Ular Laut.

188
00:12:05,050 --> 00:12:08,180
Namun, Ketua juga tak bisa
langsung menawarkan racun.

189
00:12:08,510 --> 00:12:09,950
Hanya bisa andalkan…

190
00:12:10,610 --> 00:12:14,080
Hanya racun es, masih
perlu andalkan sinar matahari?

191
00:12:14,580 --> 00:12:17,610
Ular Api Sepuluh Kepala
adalah Raja Ular.

192
00:12:17,610 --> 00:12:19,610
Ditambah dengan suhu matahari
di luar kulitnya.

193
00:12:19,610 --> 00:12:20,810
Pilnya…

194
00:12:20,810 --> 00:12:24,610
…sangat mudah untuk
mengatasi racun es Ular Laut.

195
00:12:42,210 --> 00:12:46,910
Jika ini salah paham,
apakah bisa melepaskan ketua kami?

196
00:12:49,250 --> 00:12:52,350
Karena kau menyelamatkan mereka,
kau kembalikan Xiao Wu padaku.

197
00:12:52,350 --> 00:12:53,410
Aku tak akan membunuhmu.

198
00:12:54,110 --> 00:12:55,950
Atas dasar apa kukembalikan
Xiao Wu padamu?

199
00:12:55,950 --> 00:12:56,910
Dia siapamu?

200
00:12:56,910 --> 00:12:58,480
Dia adalah calon istriku.

201
00:12:59,610 --> 00:13:00,480
Apa?

202
00:13:05,610 --> 00:13:07,650
Kenapa jika dia calon istrimu?

203
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:09,280
Melihat dia sekarang,…

204
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:11,280
…kau pasti tak melindunginya
dengan baik.

205
00:13:14,050 --> 00:13:15,910
Begini saja, kita bertaruh.

206
00:13:15,910 --> 00:13:17,250
Berlomba sekali lagi.

207
00:13:17,250 --> 00:13:19,780
Jika kau menang,
aku kembalikan Xiao Wu.

208
00:13:20,410 --> 00:13:21,910
Jika aku menang,…

209
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:23,910
…Xiao Wu tinggal
di kelompok bajak lautku.

210
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:26,350
Aku tak akan jadikan
Xiao Wu sebagai taruhan.

211
00:13:26,350 --> 00:13:26,950
Begini saja.

212
00:13:26,950 --> 00:13:27,910
Aku mengalah.

213
00:13:28,450 --> 00:13:29,580
Sekarang kulepaskan kamu.

214
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:32,510
Lalu, aku tak pakai teknik roh.

215
00:13:32,510 --> 00:13:33,410
Kau bebas.

216
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:35,280
Dalam waktu setengah jam,…

217
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:38,310
…jika aku menangkapmu lagi,
anggap aku menang.

218
00:13:38,380 --> 00:13:40,450
Mulai sekarang,
kau memanggilku jadi Ketua.

219
00:13:41,710 --> 00:13:43,910
Sebaliknya jika aku kalah,
terserah padamu.

220
00:13:44,350 --> 00:13:45,110
Bagaimana?

221
00:13:45,110 --> 00:13:46,080
Mimpi!

222
00:13:46,580 --> 00:13:48,350
Tak perlu teknik roh
juga mau menangkapku?

223
00:13:48,710 --> 00:13:49,550
Baik.

224
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:50,980
Aku bertaruh denganmu.

225
00:13:53,850 --> 00:13:54,550
Mulai saja.

226
00:13:58,010 --> 00:13:58,980
Ketua.

227
00:13:58,980 --> 00:14:00,550
Kami lindungi kamu!

228
00:14:00,910 --> 00:14:01,690
Saudara sekalian!

229
00:14:01,690 --> 00:14:02,450
Bagus!

230
00:14:02,580 --> 00:14:04,950
Jika menang, kutraktir kalian
minum arak dan makan daging!

231
00:14:06,650 --> 00:14:09,080
Teknik Ratusan Senjata
Rahasia Sekte Tang.

232
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:11,610
Kelopak Bunga Dewi.

233
00:14:24,380 --> 00:14:25,517
Kelopak Bunga Dewi…

234
00:14:25,930 --> 00:14:28,110
…sebagai Senjata Rahasia
dasar dari Sekte Tang,…

235
00:14:28,380 --> 00:14:29,610
…meski kekuatannya tak tinggi…

236
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:31,610
…tapi bisa mengendalikan
dengan baik.

237
00:14:32,050 --> 00:14:34,050
Kebetulan menutup
titik akupuntur Ma.

238
00:14:42,580 --> 00:14:45,350
Aku tak percaya tak bisa
menghindarimu di pulauku.

239
00:14:49,510 --> 00:14:52,180
Memfokuskan perhatian
dari Tulang Kepala Kebijaksanaan.

240
00:15:01,380 --> 00:15:03,610
Medan Biru Perak sudah menguncimu.

241
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:05,580
Kau tak bisa lari.

242
00:15:59,950 --> 00:16:01,350
Leluhur Roh?

243
00:16:09,110 --> 00:16:10,510
Mau menangkapku?

244
00:16:10,510 --> 00:16:12,110
Masih terlalu payah.

245
00:16:19,250 --> 00:16:20,080
Benarkah?

246
00:16:21,780 --> 00:16:25,650
Kali ini kulihat kau masih
bisa lari ke mana.

247
00:16:33,180 --> 00:16:34,280
Sudah sampai di pantai.

248
00:16:34,280 --> 00:16:35,680
Dia adalah master roh darat.

249
00:16:35,680 --> 00:16:38,210
Asalkan aku masuk ke laut,
dia tak bisa menemukanku.

250
00:16:44,910 --> 00:16:47,310
Sepertinya ada pendapatan lain.

251
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:51,150
Seperti keinginanmu.

252
00:16:52,450 --> 00:16:54,190
Bagaimana dia bisa tahu
jelas gerakanku?

253
00:17:00,710 --> 00:17:02,350
Cahaya Ungu Dewa

254
00:17:04,710 --> 00:17:05,510
Kau curang.

255
00:17:05,510 --> 00:17:07,780
Aku tak bilang tak boleh
pakai teknik tulang roh.

256
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:09,150
Mengaku kalah saja.

257
00:17:10,150 --> 00:17:11,480
Pergi mati saja.

258
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:14,310
Teknik roh ke-6, Ular Hantu Neraka.

259
00:17:36,350 --> 00:17:38,910
Bocah, kau sudah kalah.

260
